title: Roller Skate Crop Top, Crop Tee, Skate T-Shirt, Roller Skating Tee, Graphic Tee, Black And White Top, Activewear, Gift For Roller Skater
description:
The Roll Grow Empower crop tee, inspired by the carefree spirit of roller skating and the fearless girl skate gangs. Unique design by ChillaGoods. Extra comfort during rad skate sessions.
 We source products and fabrics from ethical brands and suppliers that comply to labor, environmental, and safety standards. 
 SHIPPING

 days delivery

 EVERYWHERE ELSE --> 2-7 work days processing time, 3-10 days delivery

title: Fanny Pack, Roller Skate Accessories, Roller Skate Bum Bag, Gift For Skater, Disco Bag, White Waist Bag with Black Skater Illustration
description:
A RadGal bum bag that keeps your hands free while skating! All your essentials can fit in it while your cruising down the street or the skate park. Illustration by SlavenaMustArt. Featuring small inside pocket and adjustable straps.

Ready to ship!

• 100% polyester
• Dimensions: H 6.5'' (16cm), W 13'' (33cm), D 2¾'' (7cm)
• Water-resistant material
• Top zipper with 2 sliders
• Small inner pocket without zipper
• Silky lining, piped inside hems
• 1¼'' wide adjustable straps with plastic strap regulators

CARE INSTRUCTIONS
Machine wash on low temperature.

title: Retro Roller Skate High Socks
description:
Roller skate socks made from combed cotton. Athletic socks designed to provide you with comfort during skating.

▸Specially developed for intensive sport
▸Anatomic structure
▸Smooth leg with bandage and anti-slip effect
▸Lower part of foot in terry for absorbing the physical load
▸Ribbed strips on the arch of foot with bandage and anti-slip effect
▸Comfort seam of toes on linking
▸Composition: 85% combed cotton; 15% polyamide
▸Made in Europe

title: Disco Ball Helmet
description:
This decorative disco helmet is perfect for bike parties or every day cycling.

DESIGN: multiple air vents, special aerodynamic design and breathable foam, this adults skateboard helmet help reduce sweating and feel cool, which is suitable for skate boarding, roller skating, biking, cycling, scooter BMX etc.

ADJUSTABLE STRAP: Multiple adjustable elastic straps and velcro closures for secure. This helmet pads have two lines of elastic velcro straps for the size adjustment, could be flexible to different sizes for adults.


Note: While the base helmet meets safety regulations, I cannot guarantee the safety of this decorative helmet once mirrors have been added.

description:
Disco ball Festival Visor

Perfect for festivals, photoshoots, parties, and anyone with a life less ordinary!

We specialize in wearable art and disco ball chic. We hold stock of our best-selling addition for super quick delivery!
